From ad48234e4f0765f6b19edc0fc3f95b556c5efaed Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Aniruddha Mishra <anirmish@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Wed, 9 Jul 2025 08:43:14 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM: DP: wifi: ath12k: Add support for Rx WBM Error
 stats

1. Add support for DP Telemetry in Rx WBM Err path.
At Soc level,
  RXDMA Errors,
  REO Erros and
  Drop reason are populated
At peer level,
  RXDMA Errors and REO Erros are populated per peer.

2. Add debugfs support for these soc level stats
   Using "device_dp_stats"

Sample Output:

